Image Prompt:
Create an ethereal and majestic depiction of the word "Elohim" from the Bible. Show a divine and transcendent representation with glowing light emanating from the word, surrounded by celestial elements like stars and clouds. Capture the essence of this Hebrew term symbolizing the supreme God in Christian faith, conveying a sense of reverence and awe through a visually striking and spiritually uplifting composition.
